## UTM Templates by Channel {#templates}

### Paid Search (Google Ads)

Use auto-tagging (GCLID) for Google Ads. Manual UTMs are a backup or for non-Google search engines.

```
?utm_source=google&utm_medium=cpc&utm_campaign=[campaign_name]&utm_term=[keyword]&utm_content=[ad_group]
```

### Paid Social (Meta Ads)

```
?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=paid_social&utm_campaign={{campaign.name}}&utm_content={{ad.name}}
```

Use Meta's dynamic URL parameters (double curly braces) to auto-populate values from ad settings.

### Email Campaigns

```
?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=[campaign_name]&utm_content=[link_location]
```

Example: `?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=weekly_digest_20250315&utm_content=hero_cta`

### Organic Social

```
?utm_source=[platform]&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=[campaign_name]&utm_content=[post_type]
```

Example: `?utm_source=linkedin&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=thought_leadership&utm_content=carousel_post`

### Partner and Affiliate

```
?utm_source=partner_[name]&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=[campaign_name]&utm_content=[placement]
```

### QR Codes

```
?utm_source=[location]&utm_medium=qr&utm_campaign=[campaign_name]&utm_content=[material_type]
```

Example: `?utm_source=conference_booth&utm_medium=qr&utm_campaign=saas_expo_2025&utm_content=brochure`

